    "This is a surprising result, since typically poorer countries are considered to be more likely to be effected by climate change.",
    "But our results would indicate that this distinction within our modeling context may have been over emphasized.",
    "It may be the case that climate change is a more recent phenomenon and its impact is different in more recent decades.",
    "We examined the exogenous impact therefore of country-specific and the global climate risks on GDP growth from 1950 to 2020 in a separate empirical model.",
